Losing Control;;1998;;R;;Mystery,Romance,Thriller;;4.4;;Julie Jordan;;Kira Reed Lorsch,Doug Jeffery,Anneliza Scott,Clay Greenbush,Jennifer Ludlow;;After being dumped by her fiance, Kim, a novelist has been suffering from writer's block and her publisher, Alexa is forcing her to finish the book. One night at a restaurant, a stranger sits at her table and soon she finds herself falling for him. But he leads her into sexual adventures that are, at first, thrilling, but soon becomes increasingly dangerous.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0163069/